SUMMARY:The Misinformation Challenge – How to Rebuild Trust in a
  Post-Truth World - by Evidence For Democracy
LOCATION:Virtual
DESCRIPTION:More info:
  https://evidencefordemocracy.ca/webinar-the-misinformation-challenge-how-
 to-rebuild-trust-in-a-post-truth-world/\n\nHosted by Evidence For
  Democracy (https://evidencefordemocracy.ca)\n\nAccording to Canada’s
  Foreign Interference Commissioner\, misinformation and disinformation
  pose the single greatest threat to Canadian democracy today. This webinar
  highlights the evolution of misinformation across Canada\, and provides
  important policy recommendations for addressing misinformation challenges
  and concerns.
END:VEVENT
